
Agriculture Portal 

Database :

1. user table : for registration 
  fields:
    id, first_name,last_name, email,password,confirmPassword, mobile, dob, address.
    
2. products:
  > vegitables table: 
   fields:
    id, vegitable_name, vegitable_price, vegitable_quantity.
    
    
    > pesticieds table: 
   fields:
    id, pesticied_name, pesticied_price, pesticied_quantity.
    
    
     > firtilizers table: 
   fields:
    id, firtilizer_name, firtilizer_price, firtilizer_quantity.
3.orders table:
   id, customer_id, product_name, product_price, product_totalprice,product_quantity, customer_address,order_date(date+time)
    
    
    
   
    
    
    
